c0000000
00:00:01.670 --> 00:00:03.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] I'm traveling
with you for this.</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:03.210 --> 00:00:04.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>An old friend.</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:05.300 --> 00:00:06.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He left my village
ten years ago,</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:07.010 --> 00:00:08.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and it's time we saw
each other again.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:16.850 --> 00:00:18.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you figure out
where Gorilla went?</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:20.770 --> 00:00:22.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Tur.</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:22.770 --> 00:00:23.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] It's a trading city
in the middle</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:24.070 --> 00:00:25.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the Northern Lands.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:26.030 --> 00:00:28.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] That's a long way
to the east from here.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:28.400 --> 00:00:31.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And in the exact
opposite direction of Auberst.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:32.370 --> 00:00:33.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:42.670 --> 00:00:43.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:44.750 --> 00:00:47.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I came with you on this journey
for a chance to find him.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:48.340 --> 00:00:49.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know that.</b></Default>

c0000014
00:00:50.930 --> 00:00:53.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The sun is going to set
any minute now.</b></Default>

c0000015
00:00:53.760 --> 00:00:56.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can't this decision wait
until the morning?</b></Default>

c0000016
00:00:58.730 --> 00:01:00.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I asked the villagers
about a cabin.</b></Default>

c0000017
00:01:01.440 --> 00:01:03.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They have one free,
and it's all ours.</b></Default>

c0000018
00:01:03.940 --> 00:01:05.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Thank you.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:01:08.490 --> 00:01:11.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:56.970 --> 00:02:58.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I come bearing firewood.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:58.760 --> 00:03:02.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I come bearing dinner.
You're all very welcome.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:03:05.270 --> 00:03:06.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My hands are freezing.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:03:06.900 --> 00:03:08.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
It has gotten rather cold out.</b></Default>

c0000024
00:03:09.770 --> 00:03:10.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My goodness.</b></Default>

c0000025
00:03:11.650 --> 00:03:14.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm impressed.
This might be a new record.</b></Default>

c0000026
00:03:14.950 --> 00:03:16.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shivering]</b></Default>

c0000027
00:03:18.450 --> 00:03:19.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Let me see.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:03:20.200 --> 00:03:22.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really weren't kidding.
They're icicles.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:03:22.870 --> 00:03:23.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Aren't they?</b></Default>

c0000030
00:03:23.910 --> 00:03:24.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oof.
[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000031
00:03:27.920 --> 00:03:29.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

c0000032
00:03:29.250 --> 00:03:30.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're a monster!</b></Default>

c0000033
00:03:30.840 --> 00:03:32.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Definitely a new record.</b></Default>

c0000034
00:03:32.460 --> 00:03:34.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Yeah.
They're frozen.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:03:34.550 --> 00:03:35.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ridiculous.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:03:42.310 --> 00:03:43.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] It's snowing.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:03:44.560 --> 00:03:47.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Will we need to wait for winter
to pass this time around?</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:48.060 --> 00:03:50.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Well, this time there
aren't any steep mountains</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:50.310 --> 00:03:51.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for us to cross.</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:52.150 --> 00:03:54.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unless a serious blizzard
blows our way,</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:54.190 --> 00:03:55.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we should be all right.</b></Default>

c0000042
00:04:00.950 --> 00:04:02.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Looks serious.</b></Default>

c0000043
00:04:02.370 --> 00:04:04.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] Yup, that, it does.
[STARK] Does indeed.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:04:05.250 --> 00:04:06.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE CABIN OWNER 17A]
In this region,</b></Default>

c0000045
00:04:06.330 --> 00:04:08.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a wave so strong
could last an entire month.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:04:09.040 --> 00:04:10.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't recommend
venturing far.</b></Default>

c0000047
00:04:11.630 --> 00:04:14.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Feel free to use the cabin
until it passes over.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:04:18.720 --> 00:04:21.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's up to you, Sein.
Should we try and leave?</b></Default>

c0000049
00:04:21.220 --> 00:04:23.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You already know
the answer to that.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:04:23.720 --> 00:04:26.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, we're stuck here
until the cold lets up.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:04:26.350 --> 00:04:27.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure seems like it.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:04:28.770 --> 00:04:29.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] At least
we're trapped in a place</b></Default>

c0000053
00:04:30.060 --> 00:04:31.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with bars and shops.</b></Default>

c0000054
00:04:31.980 --> 00:04:33.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The cabin's large.</b></Default>

c0000055
00:04:33.770 --> 00:04:36.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Better than that mountaintop
hovel we stayed in before.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:04:37.860 --> 00:04:39.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And more important
than anything else,</b></Default>

c0000057
00:04:40.030 --> 00:04:41.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this village has
a lovely magic shop</b></Default>

c0000058
00:04:41.910 --> 00:04:43.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>run by a shady old man.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:04:44.700 --> 00:04:47.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] In my experience,
shops like those often have</b></Default>

c0000060
00:04:47.160 --> 00:04:50.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>legendary-level spells
lurking in the shadows.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:04:50.580 --> 00:04:52.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This delay should give me
ample time</b></Default>

c0000062
00:04:52.330 --> 00:04:53.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to explore it's depths.</b></Default>

c0000063
00:04:54.340 --> 00:04:56.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Legendary-level magic?</b></Default>

c0000064
00:04:56.550 --> 00:04:58.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you already run
into some spells like that?</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:58.930 --> 00:05:00.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Mm-hmm.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:05:00.340 --> 00:05:02.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We found one great spell
to get rid of mold,</b></Default>

c0000067
00:05:02.850 --> 00:05:05.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and another to eradicate
those tough oil stains.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:05:06.270 --> 00:05:07.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Incredible.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:05:07.560 --> 00:05:08.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000070
00:05:08.850 --> 00:05:09.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Find more.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:05:10.020 --> 00:05:12.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Those little spells have been
nothing short of life changing.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:05:12.980 --> 00:05:15.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They sound more like
granny's tips and tricks.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:05:15.940 --> 00:05:18.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In any case, all we can do now
is wait it out.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:05:18.690 --> 00:05:21.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To underestimate the winters
of the Northern Lands</b></Default>

c0000075
00:05:21.200 --> 00:05:22.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is to die a bitter death</b></Default>

c0000076
00:05:23.370 --> 00:05:24.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Truly.</b></Default>

c0000077
00:05:24.490 --> 00:05:26.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It almost cost us Mister Stark,</b></Default>

c0000078
00:05:26.540 --> 00:05:28.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but that lesson
has been learned.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:05:28.830 --> 00:05:31.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] I'm from
the Northern Lands, remember?</b></Default>

c0000080
00:05:31.170 --> 00:05:32.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've known that since birth.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:05:35.500 --> 00:05:36.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, then.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:36.590 --> 00:05:37.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looks like our time together</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:37.840 --> 00:05:39.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>hasn't quite run out yet
after all.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:42.510 --> 00:05:45.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000085
00:06:09.450 --> 00:06:11.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE CABIN OWNER] This wave
should be blowing over soon.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:06:12.080 --> 00:06:15.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Before long, you adventurers
can continue on your journey.</b></Default>

c0000087
00:06:15.380 --> 00:06:17.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I guess you're right.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:06:18.420 --> 00:06:19.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, no.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:06:19.420 --> 00:06:22.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We didn't spend any of our
"time together" together.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:06:23.760 --> 00:06:25.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Sein?
[SEIN] Huh?</b></Default>

c0000091
00:06:25.510 --> 00:06:26.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>May I borrow you?</b></Default>

c0000092
00:06:27.180 --> 00:06:28.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Must be something important.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:06:29.390 --> 00:06:31.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not often you see Frieren
at a tavern.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:06:32.430 --> 00:06:35.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fern and Stark are acting more
strangely than they usually do.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:06:36.270 --> 00:06:37.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I believe
that they're fighting.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:06:38.190 --> 00:06:39.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could you mediate?</b></Default>

c0000097
00:06:39.820 --> 00:06:41.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It doesn't cost me to say yes.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:06:41.900 --> 00:06:43.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But why was I
your first thought?</b></Default>

c0000099
00:06:43.950 --> 00:06:46.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because being a peacemaker
is more of a priest job.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:06:47.740 --> 00:06:48.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] Is it?</b></Default>

c0000101
00:06:50.240 --> 00:06:51.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whining]</b></Default>

c0000102
00:06:55.580 --> 00:06:57.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What a sorry state of affairs.</b></Default>

c0000103
00:06:57.920 --> 00:07:00.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey. So, who did what to whom?</b></Default>

c0000104
00:07:00.880 --> 00:07:02.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was all
Mister Stark's fault.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:07:03.260 --> 00:07:06.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yup. Always has been,
always will be.</b></Default>

c0000106
00:07:07.350 --> 00:07:09.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] We won't get anywhere
like this.</b></Default>

c0000107
00:07:12.220 --> 00:07:14.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I need to speak with
each of you, one at a time.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:07:17.730 --> 00:07:18.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000109
00:07:23.690 --> 00:07:24.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000110
00:07:25.030 --> 00:07:27.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what happened in there?</b></Default>

c0000111
00:07:28.530 --> 00:07:30.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You remember that time
Fern touched my cheek?</b></Default>

c0000112
00:07:31.330 --> 00:07:32.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When we first arrived here,</b></Default>

c0000113
00:07:32.620 --> 00:07:34.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and her hands
were record-level cold?</b></Default>

c0000114
00:07:34.500 --> 00:07:36.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yeah. I remember.</b></Default>

c0000115
00:07:37.830 --> 00:07:40.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, today I tried to get her
back for it,</b></Default>

c0000116
00:07:40.380 --> 00:07:42.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she didn't like
that too much.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:07:43.510 --> 00:07:45.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] Come on,
are you a child?</b></Default>

c0000118
00:07:45.800 --> 00:07:47.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Sein sighs]</b></Default>

c0000119
00:07:47.760 --> 00:07:49.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've known my share of women,</b></Default>

c0000120
00:07:49.140 --> 00:07:51.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and none of them've welcomed
an uninvited hand to the face.</b></Default>

c0000121
00:07:53.350 --> 00:07:54.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] What do you
want to do about it?</b></Default>

c0000122
00:07:55.600 --> 00:07:57.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd like to make up with her
if I can.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:07:58.480 --> 00:07:59.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Listen, Stark.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:08:00.110 --> 00:08:03.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unlike me, you're actually
a good person at your core.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:08:03.150 --> 00:08:05.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be honest and tell her
how you feel.</b></Default>

c0000126
00:08:05.860 --> 00:08:07.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you want to make up
with the girl,</b></Default>

c0000127
00:08:07.320 --> 00:08:09.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then you're gonna have
to be the one to tell her that.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:08:10.240 --> 00:08:13.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're a big boy now, and
Frieren's not one to mediate.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:08:15.160 --> 00:08:17.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Trust me, I know.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:08:17.370 --> 00:08:19.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll apologize to Fern.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:08:21.340 --> 00:08:23.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] Stark feels bad
about what he did.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:08:23.920 --> 00:08:25.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's just a dumb kid.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:08:25.670 --> 00:08:27.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And he didn't mean you
any harm.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:08:27.970 --> 00:08:29.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure you're right.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:08:29.840 --> 00:08:32.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think that I'm ready
to apologize.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:08:32.470 --> 00:08:33.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was stubborn.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:08:34.850 --> 00:08:37.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm the one who started it all
in the first place.</b></Default>

c0000138
00:08:37.730 --> 00:08:40.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't even mind the fact
that he touched me.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:08:40.940 --> 00:08:44.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's just,
the arm he used to restrain</b></Default>

c0000140
00:08:44.570 --> 00:08:46.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my shoulder was so strong.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:08:48.200 --> 00:08:51.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] I guess I was startled
and a little scared.</b></Default>

c0000142
00:08:53.620 --> 00:08:55.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] Do you not like Stark?</b></Default>

c0000143
00:08:56.250 --> 00:08:58.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why would you ever ask
such a thing?</b></Default>

c0000144
00:08:58.580 --> 00:09:00.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does it seem that way?</b></Default>

c0000145
00:09:00.710 --> 00:09:03.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Go. Tell him he shouldn't be
grabbing you with full force</b></Default>

c0000146
00:09:03.590 --> 00:09:04.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and make up with him.</b></Default>

c0000147
00:09:06.670 --> 00:09:08.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be gentler with me, please.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:09:08.510 --> 00:09:09.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] I'm sorry.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:09:14.680 --> 00:09:16.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Those two
should just date already!</b></Default>

c0000150
00:09:19.060 --> 00:09:20.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not sure
what you did in there,</b></Default>

c0000151
00:09:20.480 --> 00:09:22.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I can tell that you worked
your very hardest, Sein.</b></Default>

c0000152
00:09:24.270 --> 00:09:26.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Thanks for the help.
Good job.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:09:27.280 --> 00:09:28.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

c0000154
00:09:28.740 --> 00:09:30.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] You know, Frieren,</b></Default>

c0000155
00:09:30.280 --> 00:09:33.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're the only one who still
praises me like I'm a kid.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:09:33.700 --> 00:09:35.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's because you are a kid.</b></Default>

c0000157
00:09:36.910 --> 00:09:39.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Eh. I suppose it isn't
all that bad.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:09:42.500 --> 00:09:45.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] Hey. I've been thinking
about something.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:09:46.670 --> 00:09:49.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why do you trouble yourself
with the likes of me?</b></Default>

c0000160
00:09:49.510 --> 00:09:52.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I still don't know why you
invited me to travel with you.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:09:53.840 --> 00:09:54.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE TOWNSPERSON 17B]
Should I try again?</b></Default>

c0000162
00:09:55.180 --> 00:09:57.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Must be my aversion
to my own kind.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:09:58.220 --> 00:10:00.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The way you refused
to go on an adventure?</b></Default>

c0000164
00:10:00.980 --> 00:10:02.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It reminded me of myself</b></Default>

c0000165
00:10:02.560 --> 00:10:04.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before I left to defeat
the Demon King.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:10:05.230 --> 00:10:06.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
That angered me.</b></Default>

c0000167
00:10:07.440 --> 00:10:10.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When something angers me,
I don't cart it across the map.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:10:10.650 --> 00:10:12.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not certain,</b></Default>

c0000169
00:10:12.490 --> 00:10:14.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I think what I really
wanted deep down</b></Default>

c0000170
00:10:14.570 --> 00:10:15.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was to give you a reason.</b></Default>

c0000171
00:10:16.660 --> 00:10:18.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
What does that mean?</b></Default>

c0000172
00:10:20.450 --> 00:10:21.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If he had been there,</b></Default>

c0000173
00:10:21.660 --> 00:10:23.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's what Himmel the Hero
would've done.</b></Default>

c0000174
00:10:26.210 --> 00:10:28.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come, Frieren.
Take my hand.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:10:29.550 --> 00:10:31.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let me be your reason
to go on a journey.</b></Default>

c0000176
00:10:37.720 --> 00:10:39.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They gave me courage
to go into the world</b></Default>

c0000177
00:10:39.640 --> 00:10:41.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd long hidden from.</b></Default>

c0000178
00:10:41.270 --> 00:10:44.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They also taught me the joy
of spending time with friends.</b></Default>

c0000179
00:10:46.230 --> 00:10:47.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me, Sein.</b></Default>

c0000180
00:10:47.730 --> 00:10:49.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Have you felt that joy?</b></Default>

c0000181
00:10:51.990 --> 00:10:52.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000182
00:10:53.950 --> 00:10:55.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN]
This has been a lot of fun.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:10:55.820 --> 00:10:58.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000184
00:11:07.880 --> 00:11:09.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll change the world
like Himmel.</b></Default>

c0000185
00:11:09.630 --> 00:11:11.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be an unforgettable hero.</b></Default>

c0000186
00:11:12.130 --> 00:11:14.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't dwell in the past
when you have the present.</b></Default>

c0000187
00:11:15.260 --> 00:11:16.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Trust me.</b></Default>

c0000188
00:11:16.550 --> 00:11:19.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Since intent couldn't be
assured with a look or a touch,</b></Default>

c0000189
00:11:19.560 --> 00:11:21.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I decided to trust her words.</b></Default>

c0000190
00:11:21.760 --> 00:11:23.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STUBBORN] Gorilla talked
about you all the time.</b></Default>

c0000191
00:11:23.680 --> 00:11:25.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>His friend, Goatee Priest.</b></Default>

c0000192
00:11:26.600 --> 00:11:28.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He said the two of you
would become heroes</b></Default>

c0000193
00:11:28.980 --> 00:11:32.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>whose names would be
remembered forever. Foolish.</b></Default>

c0000194
00:11:35.740 --> 00:11:38.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000195
00:11:41.120 --> 00:11:42.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales]</b></Default>

c0000196
00:11:43.540 --> 00:11:44.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000197
00:11:56.590 --> 00:11:58.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] I'm not going to live
with regrets anymore.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:11:59.390 --> 00:12:01.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've decided to go
after Gorilla.</b></Default>

c0000199
00:12:02.810 --> 00:12:04.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I figured as much.</b></Default>

c0000200
00:12:05.310 --> 00:12:06.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You all take care.</b></Default>

c0000201
00:12:09.730 --> 00:12:10.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] See you later.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:12:13.070 --> 00:12:14.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] Later.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:12:22.240 --> 00:12:24.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That must've been the quickest
goodbye I've ever seen.</b></Default>

c0000204
00:12:25.370 --> 00:12:28.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, unlike you two,
our friend Sein is an adult.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:12:28.870 --> 00:12:30.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure he'll be fine.</b></Default>

c0000206
00:12:49.190 --> 00:12:51.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SEIN] It gets quiet fast
when you're on your own.</b></Default>

c0000207
00:12:54.570 --> 00:12:57.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000208
00:13:03.370 --> 00:13:06.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Stark (song) humming]</b></Default>

c0000209
00:13:14.170 --> 00:13:15.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? Really?</b></Default>

c0000210
00:13:16.840 --> 00:13:19.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] That's strange.
She'd usually be up by now.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:13:20.550 --> 00:13:22.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We have been walking
a lot recently.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:13:22.510 --> 00:13:23.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess she's worn out.</b></Default>

c0000213
00:13:33.560 --> 00:13:35.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[blows]</b></Default>

c0000214
00:13:36.320 --> 00:13:37.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[slurps]</b></Default>

c0000215
00:13:38.610 --> 00:13:40.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Eh. It's good enough.</b></Default>

c0000216
00:13:42.410 --> 00:13:44.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, your breakfast
is ready, Fern.</b></Default>

c0000217
00:13:45.200 --> 00:13:46.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Get up or I'll eat it.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:13:48.040 --> 00:13:50.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? Hello?</b></Default>

c0000219
00:13:51.080 --> 00:13:53.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breathing heavily]</b></Default>

c0000220
00:13:55.330 --> 00:13:57.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Frieren? I need help.</b></Default>

c0000221
00:13:57.460 --> 00:13:58.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000222
00:13:58.670 --> 00:14:00.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just gimme twelve more hours.</b></Default>

c0000223
00:14:00.880 --> 00:14:03.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah right. Not even you could
sleep for that long.</b></Default>

c0000224
00:14:03.930 --> 00:14:06.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm worried Fern
might not be feeling so good.</b></Default>

c0000225
00:14:06.930 --> 00:14:08.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[snoring]</b></Default>

c0000226
00:14:09.020 --> 00:14:10.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000227
00:14:11.140 --> 00:14:12.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>C'mon.</b></Default>

c0000228
00:14:15.270 --> 00:14:16.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[snoring]</b></Default>

c0000229
00:14:18.820 --> 00:14:20.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're a monster.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:14:22.400 --> 00:14:24.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, seems you have a fever.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:14:25.360 --> 00:14:27.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What you need is warmth
and rest.</b></Default>

c0000232
00:14:29.870 --> 00:14:32.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's see.</b></Default>

c0000233
00:14:36.290 --> 00:14:38.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Hmm. That's odd.</b></Default>

c0000234
00:14:38.550 --> 00:14:40.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] I got some water.</b></Default>

c0000235
00:14:40.510 --> 00:14:41.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Found it.</b></Default>

c0000236
00:14:41.800 --> 00:14:43.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? What is that?</b></Default>

c0000237
00:14:43.590 --> 00:14:45.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sein left us these notes.</b></Default>

c0000238
00:14:45.220 --> 00:14:47.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Should shed some light on herbs
around here.</b></Default>

c0000239
00:14:47.890 --> 00:14:49.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aw, thanks, Sein.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:14:49.810 --> 00:14:51.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Magic will help identify
her ailment,</b></Default>

c0000241
00:14:52.140 --> 00:14:54.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and this book
will help find the cure.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:14:54.850 --> 00:14:56.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought
identifying sicknesses</b></Default>

c0000243
00:14:56.480 --> 00:14:57.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was the magic of the Goddess.</b></Default>

c0000244
00:14:58.610 --> 00:15:00.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Before, you said only someone</b></Default>

c0000245
00:15:00.400 --> 00:15:02.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with a holy scripture
could cast it.</b></Default>

c0000246
00:15:02.780 --> 00:15:05.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's exactly why I keep
a scripture on hand.</b></Default>

c0000247
00:15:05.280 --> 00:15:06.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-What?
-Huh?</b></Default>

c0000248
00:15:10.660 --> 00:15:12.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
You're using it as a pot stand?</b></Default>

c0000249
00:15:14.750 --> 00:15:16.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I may not be cut
from priestly cloth,</b></Default>

c0000250
00:15:17.040 --> 00:15:19.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but even I can identify
simple illnesses.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:15:20.960 --> 00:15:22.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The complex ones
are a different story.</b></Default>

c0000252
00:15:23.090 --> 00:15:24.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Reassuring.</b></Default>

c0000253
00:15:26.340 --> 00:15:28.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Good. It's just a cold.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:15:30.180 --> 00:15:32.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now to determine
which herbs to forage for.</b></Default>

c0000255
00:15:34.770 --> 00:15:37.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thinking back, I seem to recall
a place nearby</b></Default>

c0000256
00:15:37.770 --> 00:15:39.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>where I gathered herbs
with Himmel and the others.</b></Default>

c0000257
00:15:41.150 --> 00:15:42.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Sounds good.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:15:42.400 --> 00:15:44.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But first, let's get her
someplace out of the cold.</b></Default>

c0000259
00:15:45.110 --> 00:15:46.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Smart thinking.</b></Default>

c0000260
00:15:52.870 --> 00:15:54.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cow mooing]</b></Default>

c0000261
00:15:58.040 --> 00:15:59.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh?</b></Default>

c0000262
00:16:06.420 --> 00:16:08.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
You're a lifesaver, ma'am.</b></Default>

c0000263
00:16:09.050 --> 00:16:10.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't think that anybody</b></Default>

c0000264
00:16:10.390 --> 00:16:12.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>lived this deep
in the mountains.</b></Default>

c0000265
00:16:12.640 --> 00:16:15.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There was a village here
when I stopped by before.</b></Default>

c0000266
00:16:15.680 --> 00:16:18.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That village hasn't been around
for decades.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:16:18.650 --> 00:16:20.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was a prestigious
little spot, you know.</b></Default>

c0000268
00:16:20.770 --> 00:16:23.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The hero himself
even paid it a visit once!</b></Default>

c0000269
00:16:24.070 --> 00:16:26.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, feel free
to make yourselves at home.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:16:27.530 --> 00:16:28.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you.</b></Default>

c0000271
00:16:29.410 --> 00:16:30.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's a tree near here, yes?</b></Default>

c0000272
00:16:31.030 --> 00:16:32.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A great icicle cherry blossom?</b></Default>

c0000273
00:16:33.370 --> 00:16:35.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes. Just a bit to the north.</b></Default>

c0000274
00:16:36.330 --> 00:16:38.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I must warn you, though,
it can be tricky to get to.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:16:39.460 --> 00:16:40.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can manage.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:16:41.290 --> 00:16:42.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
I've been there before.</b></Default>

c0000277
00:16:45.340 --> 00:16:47.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE VILLAGER 17A] Well,
I'll be working if you need me.</b></Default>

c0000278
00:16:50.260 --> 00:16:52.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're going to go gather
some ingredients.</b></Default>

c0000279
00:16:52.640 --> 00:16:54.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll be back
with your medicine soon.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:16:55.350 --> 00:16:57.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You haven't let go of her hand
once since we got here.</b></Default>

c0000281
00:16:58.180 --> 00:17:00.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Because she seems
to be in pain.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:17:00.690 --> 00:17:02.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When Fern is under
the weather,</b></Default>

c0000283
00:17:02.730 --> 00:17:05.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>nothing makes her feel
better than holding her hand.</b></Default>

c0000284
00:17:05.940 --> 00:17:07.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's been that way
since she was little.</b></Default>

c0000285
00:17:11.780 --> 00:17:13.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] What's wrong?</b></Default>

c0000286
00:17:14.080 --> 00:17:17.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Frieren,
you're embarrassing me.</b></Default>

c0000287
00:17:18.660 --> 00:17:19.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How so?</b></Default>

c0000288
00:17:20.460 --> 00:17:22.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] You're treating me
like a child,</b></Default>

c0000289
00:17:22.790 --> 00:17:24.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>which I am not.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:17:27.090 --> 00:17:29.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I see. You're right.</b></Default>

c0000291
00:17:33.640 --> 00:17:36.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In two years, she'll be
a full-fledged grown up.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:17:38.060 --> 00:17:41.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not long ago, she only came up
right to here on me.</b></Default>

c0000293
00:17:42.060 --> 00:17:44.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I found myself feeling
rather tall in those days.</b></Default>

c0000294
00:17:45.230 --> 00:17:46.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That sure didn't last.</b></Default>

c0000295
00:17:47.480 --> 00:17:49.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Honestly, in my heart,</b></Default>

c0000296
00:17:49.400 --> 00:17:51.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fern's still that same
little girl.</b></Default>

c0000297
00:17:52.490 --> 00:17:54.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I picture her as a child.</b></Default>

c0000298
00:17:54.320 --> 00:17:55.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Probably always will.</b></Default>

c0000299
00:17:57.200 --> 00:17:58.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aw, Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:17:59.450 --> 00:18:01.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We had better hurry up
and gather those herbs, then.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:18:02.920 --> 00:18:03.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

c0000302
00:18:05.460 --> 00:18:06.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:18:09.800 --> 00:18:12.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000304
00:18:31.780 --> 00:18:32.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
We should reach the icicle</b></Default>

c0000305
00:18:32.950 --> 00:18:34.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>cherry blossom tree soon.</b></Default>

c0000306
00:18:35.240 --> 00:18:36.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Do we need
any more ingredients?</b></Default>

c0000307
00:18:38.080 --> 00:18:39.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or is the blossom the last one?</b></Default>

c0000308
00:18:40.540 --> 00:18:42.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sort of. What we want
is the mushrooms</b></Default>

c0000309
00:18:42.750 --> 00:18:44.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that grow at the base.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:18:46.170 --> 00:18:47.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000311
00:18:57.720 --> 00:19:01.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Gorgeous. I so wish
we could've shown Fern.</b></Default>

c0000312
00:19:02.180 --> 00:19:03.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] These might be
my favorite flowers</b></Default>

c0000313
00:19:03.850 --> 00:19:05.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that bloom in winter.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:19:07.190 --> 00:19:09.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're quite poisonous,
though, so be careful.</b></Default>

c0000315
00:19:10.940 --> 00:19:14.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, what was the deal
with you holding her hand?</b></Default>

c0000316
00:19:15.530 --> 00:19:18.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Normally, you don't treat Fern
that much like a kid.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:19:19.080 --> 00:19:21.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was never my intention
to baby her.</b></Default>

c0000318
00:19:22.410 --> 00:19:24.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I simply held her hand
because it looked like</b></Default>

c0000319
00:19:24.460 --> 00:19:25.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she was hurting.</b></Default>

c0000320
00:19:27.380 --> 00:19:29.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] All these years,
and that's only way</b></Default>

c0000321
00:19:29.420 --> 00:19:31.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know to relieve her pain.</b></Default>

c0000322
00:19:33.970 --> 00:19:36.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you suppose I should've
done to help instead?</b></Default>

c0000323
00:19:39.430 --> 00:19:40.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think you have to go
with your gut</b></Default>

c0000324
00:19:40.720 --> 00:19:42.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when it comes
to things like that.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:19:43.350 --> 00:19:45.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At least, that's what my master
always did.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:19:47.730 --> 00:19:50.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everybody needs some kind of
emotional support, don't they?</b></Default>

c0000327
00:19:52.230 --> 00:19:53.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No one in their right mind
would push away</b></Default>

c0000328
00:19:54.070 --> 00:19:55.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a shoulder to lean on.</b></Default>

c0000329
00:19:56.740 --> 00:19:58.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000330
00:19:59.030 --> 00:20:00.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

c0000331
00:20:01.990 --> 00:20:03.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you think you're doing?</b></Default>

c0000332
00:20:04.160 --> 00:20:05.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were groaning a bit.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:20:06.540 --> 00:20:08.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sickness can make us
feel so helpless.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:20:09.920 --> 00:20:11.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I lost my mother
when I was young,</b></Default>

c0000335
00:20:12.210 --> 00:20:14.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but she used to hold my hand
just like this.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:20:15.550 --> 00:20:17.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
It's strangely calming.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:20:17.510 --> 00:20:19.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're treating me
the way you would a child?</b></Default>

c0000338
00:20:20.390 --> 00:20:21.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It isn't just children</b></Default>

c0000339
00:20:21.550 --> 00:20:23.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who need the occasional dose
of emotional support.</b></Default>

c0000340
00:20:26.430 --> 00:20:28.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it bothering you?</b></Default>

c0000341
00:20:28.270 --> 00:20:29.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales and exhales]</b></Default>

c0000342
00:20:29.940 --> 00:20:31.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't suppose so.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:20:31.610 --> 00:20:32.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales]</b></Default>

c0000344
00:20:32.690 --> 00:20:34.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It isn't all that bad.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:20:35.440 --> 00:20:38.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I try to be kind.
Amplifies my beauty.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:20:38.610 --> 00:20:39.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please be quiet.</b></Default>

c0000347
00:20:40.120 --> 00:20:41.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]</b></Default>

c0000348
00:20:42.160 --> 00:20:44.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At last! Medicine's ready.</b></Default>

c0000349
00:20:47.910 --> 00:20:50.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fern was only embarrassed
because I was there.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:20:50.620 --> 00:20:51.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So don't feel bad.</b></Default>

c0000351
00:20:53.170 --> 00:20:54.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course
she didn't want me to see.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:20:55.170 --> 00:20:57.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It could risk her whole
tough girl facade.</b></Default>

c0000353
00:20:58.340 --> 00:21:00.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks for your insight, Stark.</b></Default>

c0000354
00:21:01.850 --> 00:21:03.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll "go with my gut,"
as you say.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:21:05.390 --> 00:21:06.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
To repay you for your kindness,</b></Default>

c0000356
00:21:07.020 --> 00:21:09.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I vow to hold your hand
the next time you get sick.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:21:10.350 --> 00:21:12.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please don't.
That's embarrassing.</b></Default>

c0000358
00:21:13.270 --> 00:21:15.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Enough chat.
Time to gather some mushrooms.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:21:17.690 --> 00:21:19.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Heave, ho!</b></Default>

c0000360
00:21:19.820 --> 00:21:22.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That thing is way too big!
Freaky!</b></Default>

c0000361
00:21:23.030 --> 00:21:25.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Now we just add
the other ingredients,</b></Default>

c0000362
00:21:26.040 --> 00:21:29.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and mix slowly and steadily
until it's combined.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:21:29.410 --> 00:21:31.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You look like a witch!
Actually freaky!</b></Default>

c0000364
00:21:34.210 --> 00:21:35.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Open wide, Fern.</b></Default>

c0000365
00:21:45.470 --> 00:21:47.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks for the help, young man.</b></Default>

c0000366
00:21:47.470 --> 00:21:48.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're good at that.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:21:48.770 --> 00:21:50.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]
You think so?</b></Default>

c0000368
00:21:52.230 --> 00:21:55.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] It's all right.
You'll feel better soon.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:21:56.440 --> 00:21:59.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mistress Frieren,
I'm not a child anymore.</b></Default>

c0000370
00:22:00.950 --> 00:22:02.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I know.</b></Default>

c0000371
00:22:02.820 --> 00:22:04.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That much is clear.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:22:06.910 --> 00:22:08.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

c0000373
00:22:14.250 --> 00:22:16.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE VILLAGER 17A] Take care
of yourselves out there, okay?</b></Default>

c0000374
00:22:18.500 --> 00:22:21.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We will, ma'am!
Thank you for everything!</b></Default>

c0000375
00:22:22.090 --> 00:22:23.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're looking a lot better.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:22:25.470 --> 00:22:27.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks to a combination
of you two,</b></Default>

c0000377
00:22:27.720 --> 00:22:31.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mister Sein's
very generous notes, and her.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:22:31.730 --> 00:22:34.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I couldn't have picked
a better spot to get sick.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:22:34.520 --> 00:22:36.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
I was in the best of hands.</b></Default>

c0000380
00:22:37.150 --> 00:22:39.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right. Come along, now.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:22:40.650 --> 00:22:44.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Off to the city of magic.
Auberst awaits.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:22:50.250 --> 00:22:53.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000383
00:24:20.460 --> 00:24:22.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LERNEN] Might I take
a look at that?</b></Default>

c0000384
00:24:22.130 --> 00:24:23.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FALSCH]
This year's test-takers</b></Default>

c0000385
00:24:23.300 --> 00:24:24.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>seem rather exceptional.</b></Default>

c0000386
00:24:24.380 --> 00:24:25.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] I can't do this alone.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:24:25.460 --> 00:24:26.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Don't call me an old</b></Default>

c0000388
00:24:26.470 --> 00:24:27.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>mage.
[SENSE] I don't.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:24:27.340 --> 00:24:29.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GENAU] The first-class
mage exam will now begin.</b></Default>

